race.description: Lj Hooker Property Specialists 3YO Mdn Plt
race.comment: Competitive maiden. FOREVER A DIAMOND (10) has raced four times as well and looks to be close to a win, finishing runner-up the latest here when beaten a lip. Will ride the speed and give a sight again. LONGREACH DROVER (5) was safely held over in Victorian on debut in tougher company then runner-up in NSW last time. Drawn for a soft run on the inside and worth following up. FINE ACE (9) is fitter for two runs back and gave too big a start in the small field last time. Looks better placed here. STREET NYX (6) Son of Overshare from Street Goddess on debut. Well held in a recent trial. Jockey has a good strike rate for this yard so keep an eye on the betting.
